{"tid":85913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天王劉德華泰國墜馬     脊椎斷裂恐殘廢","createTime":"2017-01-18T16:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T10:28:40.000Z","uid":58099,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"575c7beef88a94a5b123ac22bd0f857fd706c5f5","tid":85913,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/c2618054d63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fc2618054d63.jpg&h=01c73fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年55歲的劉德華，16日前往泰國拍新廣告，在郊區拍攝一場騎馬的場面時，馬匹忽然發狂，劉德華不慎墮馬，更被馬匹踩到脊椎，當場腰脊骨裂，緊急送醫，但因傷勢嚴重，行動不便，須坐醫療專機回港，再接受香港醫生診治。<br />\n<br />\n據港媒報導，一位同在泰國的製作人表示，劉德華17日在距離曼谷3小時車程的寇立開工，當時有數匹馬在場，他所騎的馬忽然失控，將之拋下，落地後的劉德華又被失控的馬踩到脊椎，據聞傷勢頗為嚴重恐殘廢，目前廣告全面停拍，劉德華也將搭醫療專機返港接受專業救治"},{"pid":"5b9855f3cbb567c11d3c1524a4f28d58e144e3c6","tid":85913,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"Old news is very amazing"},{"pid":"1de3c1559b4e3ecd845da992900eee0d24fc9333","tid":85913,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a53bddc9f29e17cdc021940741fd89c4027998","tid":85913,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:11:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">恐</span></strong></span>殘廢"},{"pid":"bbb7d4e5a3849585343ec483b0e1f7794b800788","tid":85913,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1610236bd82c9c362ae058da1ea48520904916a","tid":85913,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38632143f1ecec42c0024667041ac115d89c58